        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 1–3. Chromocheilosia bicolor (Shannon &Aubertin, 1933): (1) female, scale bar not available (photo by Ximo Mengual, licence CC: BY-NC-SA). Chromocheilosia incerta (Shannon & Aubertin, 1933): (2) male, lateral view (photo by Patricia Henríquez). Scale bar = 1 mm. Chromocheilosia pubescens (Shannon & Aubertin, 1933); (3) female, lateral view (photo by Patricia Henríquez). Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4693468/files/figure.png" .

